# Distribution for CommonsBase_Dk (Windows_arm64)

Windows_arm64 has no DkML toolchain slice, so it ships no dk0/dk1 executable
and stays cache-only: this slot republishes the Dune cache alone until an
arm64 toolchain lands.

## Dk0 Dune Cache

  $ get-object CommonsBase_Dk.Dk0.DuneCache@2.4.2 -s Release.Windows_arm64 -f ${RUNTIME}/Windows_arm64-Dk0.DuneCache-2.4.2.zip
  \test(pass)
  \dk.object(abi: "Release.Windows_arm64", value-id: "oswreb5xr75zg3e7q7pqegda3bbqgsnkdfir2muqnh53xut6je5sa")\;
